  <title>3A.2 打开 / 关闭维护模式</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading3">3A.2 打开 / 关闭维护模式</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="3A.2 Turning Maintenance Mode ON OFF.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="28.00%" width="370" height="73" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:14px;">要执行 APC 维护功能，必须开启维护模式。</para>
    <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="·" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal">要打开，请按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[MAINTENANCE]</text>软键，<text style="font-weight:bold;">[MAINTENANCE]</text>软键的背景将突出显示为黄色。</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="·" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal">要关闭，请按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[MAINTENANCE]</text>软键，<text style="font-weight:bold;">[MAINTENANCE]</text>软键的背景将突出显示为黑色。</li>
    </list>
  </body>
